            "chapterTitle": "Undesirability of Riding a Camel which eats Animals' waste",
            "urn": 1624930,
            "body": "<p>Ibn 'Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) said: The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) prohibited riding a camel which eats dung, or animal or human waste.<br/><br/><b>[Abu Dawud]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
